msgid "**Parameters**"
msgstr "**Paràmetres**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_digital.rst:15
msgid ""
"**circuit** (:class:`~qilisdk.digital.circuit.Circuit`): Circuit to be "
"propagated."
msgstr ""
"**circuit** (:class:`~qilisdk.digital.circuit.Circuit`): Circuit a propagar."

